            <abstract id="ref6" label="Abstract">Field recordings made in North Carolina in 1958. Cherokee sacred formulae dealing with the ball game, portions of the ball dance, and relating to medicine and love ceremonies. The 24 formulae are given first in Cherokee by the consultant, then followed by the collector's translation and commentary. Also includes one related story given in English.</abstract>
